description.narrative: Efficient and efficient management, which contributes to Adolescent Health And Nutrition, Maternal And Newborn Health. UNICEF aims to achieve this through Evaluations, Research And Data, Operational Support To Programme Delivery, Systems Strengthening And Institution Building. This contributes to the following Country Programme result: By 2019, children, adolescents and women, especially those who belong to the most marginalized groups, have access to quality and high-impact maternal and neonatal health care with an intercultural and gender-sensitive approach.
